    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/fa88f5d0b1739583613b8e6aacb5431a.webp?t=1718316820\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br><strong>「游戏简介」</strong><br>《Phantom Breaker: Omnia》是《Phantom Breaker: Extra》的一次重大更新，而后者是 2013 年由 Mages 首发的一款 1-vs-1 单挑 2D 动漫格斗游戏。该游戏的特点是采用了两个客串角色，即《命运石之门》(Steins;Gate) 中的 Kurisu Makise 和《混沌之脑》(Chaos;Head) 中的 Rimi Sakihata，以及专为《Phantom Breaker Omnia》打造的两个全新角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/c2bc7b7f5d99e4bceae1bb35f9da87ec.poster.avif?t=1718316820\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/c2bc7b7f5d99e4bceae1bb35f9da87ec.webm?t=1718316820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/c2bc7b7f5d99e4bceae1bb35f9da87ec.mp4?t=1718316820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/d74f3df3f9256244cc2e67d3ceaa1d81.webp?t=1718316820\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br><strong>「特点」</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>20 个角色的阵容！</strong><br>包括《Phantom Breaker: Extra》中的所有角色，如《命运石之门》(Steins;Gate) 中的 Kurisu Makise 以及专为《Phantom Breaker Omnia》打造的两个全新角色。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>3 种不同的格斗风格任你选择：快速、硬派和全能</strong><br>游戏中 3 种不同的风格能陡然改变角色的速度、力量和机制。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>回归简约，重新平衡！</strong><br>由于我们全面改进并重新平衡了《Phantom Breaker: Omnia》的格斗系统，实现组合技能和特别攻击再轻松不过了。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/80c00d2b67dd05def03dc496a74a1704.poster.avif?t=1718316820\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/80c00d2b67dd05def03dc496a74a1704.webm?t=1718316820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/80c00d2b67dd05def03dc496a74a1704.mp4?t=1718316820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>双语音频！</strong><br>《Phantom Breaker》系列游戏第一次为所有角色配上了英语对白。游戏中的文字也将译为英语、日语、法语、意大利语、德语、西班牙语、简体中文和繁体中文。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>重新混录了现代风格的配乐！</strong><br>重新制作和混音了每个角色的背景音乐！此外，我们还新增了播放原始背景音乐的选项。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>完美的体验！</strong><br>玩家既可畅玩原作《Phantom Breaker》，也能沉浸于《Phantom Breaker: Extra》的故事之中。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/c874720f0bcad85ee718d2ee86a42f6f.webp?t=1718316820\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br><strong>「故事」</strong><br>一个神秘的男子出现在日本首都东京，人们只知道他叫“Phantom”，他挑唆经不起诱惑的青少年们互相撕杀，送给他们名为“聚变维度神器”的神秘高能武器。作为交换，他答应满足他们的愿望，只要他们能幸存下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/e15df8ea60db4bc56eccad5c94775853.poster.avif?t=1718316820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/e15df8ea60db4bc56eccad5c94775853.webm?t=1718316820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184560/extras/e15df8ea60db4bc56eccad5c94775853.mp4?t=1718316820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这些格斗士们浑然不知，聚变维度神器之间的猛烈碰撞导致时空扭曲，从而破坏了平行宇宙的边界。这些平行宇宙的坍塌最终会打破封印，解放 Phantom 的毁灭力量。",
